if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會裝住, 之後沙中線要改月台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩拉直完月台 準備裝啦<br />\n平時月台下底個逃生槽都改裝左黎起幕門</blockquote><br />\n預計兩年後裝第一道門，6年內應該裝得哂</blockquote><br />\n東鐵線幕門呢加野，真係講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n因為沙中線嚟緊要轉用新韓國車，門位同地鐵睇齊，但同現有嘅東鐵線列車完全唔同，所以幕門要等成條線轉用晒韓國車先可以裝，加上要keep住營運，預計應該裝好撚耐，起碼2022年先裝得晒成條線咁多個站"},{"pid":"e8a61fe53336f28bb2a20046b81efa3e1eff2d71","tid":177173,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:30:51.000Z","msg":"跳軌應該真係最痛<br />\n全身每一個百份比既肉都會被列車上既齒輪撕成碎塊<br />\n仲要唔係即死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9d6638dc39819497137001e90f468be0d8d683","tid":177173,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329000941812-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170329012705\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329000941812-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170329012705&h=82da7f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329000941812-0329_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170329012705\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329000941812-0329_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170329012705&h=b705e691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵東鐵線發生墮軌意外，凌晨零時許，上水站紅磡方向月台一名40餘歲男子墮軌，並遭列車撞倒捲困車底，消防員及救護員到場將事主救出，證實傷重死亡。警方正調查死者身分及墮軌原因。"},{"pid":"f28bc78cc2c0b4d7037293547e11cde3c93d9471","tid":177173,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"仲以為回帶post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}